    "chemicalDescription": [
      "Aspergillus/(Artemisia Capillaris/Cyanus Segetum Flower/Leaf/Stem)/(Artemisia Montana/Melissa Officinalis/Thyme Leaf/Stem) Ferment Filtrate is a filtrate of the product obtained by the fermentation of the flowers, leaves, and stems of Artemisia capillaris and Cyanus segetum; the leaves and stems of Artemisia montana, Melissa officinalis, and Thymus vulgaris (thyme); by the microorganism Aspergillus oryzae. The accepted scientific name for Cyanus segetum is Centaurea cyanus."
